"msg":"<blockquote>人地追你，你唔受，仲好意思屈返人轉頭，話人地追追吓唔追，好易放棄，你都真係好野<br />\n<br />\n我以前試過追女仔，追極對方都冇乜表示，以為佢已經有男朋友，或者唔中意我，所以放棄左追佢<br />\n<br />\n做女仔真係要醒少少。男人心態係漁翁撒網，你受就受，唔受就下一個，香港唔剩止你一個女人，唔好諗住男方會死唔斷氣死纏爛打，其實男人好易放棄，唔會浪費太多時間喺一個女人身上</blockquote><br />\n我唔鍾意個d已經講清楚左<br />\n但係我鍾意既就突然間變左 <br />\n明明傾得好地地 突然就已讀我  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可能真係好似你咁講啦 搵到下個目標 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e097002e6ebb220e76b5581e854971c61d272513","tid":151771,"uid":58998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T07:49:54.000Z","msg":"見過鬼仲唔怕黑咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n將心思放哂一個到太容易過度上心而被收兵<br />\n你都唔會只開放俾一個追啦<br />\n分散投資而係皇道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f96f7ff6f05887d3bbb911bafd3ed5f10920d85a","tid":151771,"uid":60491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T07:50:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔係淨係你等人埋黎 你覺得邊個岩就比啲signal啦屌</blockquote><br />\n啱，明知人地追緊你，你又對人有意思就講俾人知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一直等人表白嘅就唔好怪人追到一半放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能根本無追過<br />\n可能玩我架咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d964aef91f001faab17cd289413917790817a85c","tid":151771,"uid":71467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T07:51:51.000Z","msg":"你唔係啱啱先變左做小綠帽咩"},{"pid":"87da6025a0ca969241f33b4dd422ac9f3bc77b0c","tid":151771,"uid":4278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T07:52:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>近排成日喺度諗，究竟係咪自己好有問題自己唔知？點解成日遇到d男仔都會追追下唔追？<br />\n<br />\n自問的而且確都幾多男仔追緊，但係唔鍾意個d真係當朋友，絕對唔會收兵。<br />\n鍾意一個人會對佢好好，一定會比佢知，唔會好主動但係唔會若即若離咁。<br />\n<br />\n真心，如果唔係鍾意既點解又要追，追到一半又走左去，真係受夠啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n男仔們可唔可以入黎答下我，究竟點解你會追追下個女仔唔追？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSame here 啊sis <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1057118b5f49c95ad1ec7ac380d5cdfc99f70c45","tid":151771,"uid":11740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T07:52:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你要去難道我追？<br />\n追得到我共你都太累</blockquote><br />\n我只想跟你做對最穩固伴侶"},{"pid":"8295a8704ee06e870d9ddf36c81689ae97d534c5","tid":151771,"uid":2719,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T07:52:41.000Z","msg":"如果個個追完你都調頭走<br />\n就係你自己問題啦 關男人咩事"},{"pid":"65a264111aea87824937d7ee244d9f0e6b80db66","tid":151771,"uid":60491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T07:52:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你唔係啱啱先變左做小綠帽咩</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n綠帽已好久了 應該是上年差不多尾的事"},{"pid":"346ea4d51c01a3812e900c3428b79daca343f230","tid":151771,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T07:53:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可能識你耐左, 覺得你唔係佢心諗個種人, 所以走人</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0cc5253644174bff2cd850f52f1f5c3fa470e9c","tid":151771,"uid":60491,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T07:53:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果個個追完你都調頭走<br />\n就係你自己問題啦 關男人咩事</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我以為我地雙方有好感<br />\n原來係我自作多情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19fc94d5a3df97c52996bad5285f8352fb17c755","tid":151771,"uid":60491,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T07:54:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSame here 啊sis <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你係唔係都係傾得好地地 無啦啦俾人藍剔"},{"pid":"1ea139f8921105db7b9ab940084c83b6a9bbde46","tid":151771,"uid":73848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T07:54:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果個個追完你都調頭走<br />\n就係你自己問題啦 關男人咩事</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我以為我地雙方有好感<br />\n原來係我自作多情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你鍾意人唔追番人？扮受害者屌你老味臭"},{"pid":"640916af9319d969a24788a6d61359b8fa964cc4","tid":151771,"uid":60491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T07:57:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果個個追完你都調頭走<br />\n就係你自己問題啦 關男人咩事</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我以為我地雙方有好感<br />\n原來係我自作多情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你鍾意人唔追番人？扮受害者屌你老味臭</blockquote><br />\nChur住人 唔係會令人覺得好煩咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我驚佢嫌我煩 block埋我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fcf28c939b6192ddb7493b793e04dbd1f78fd7e","tid":151771,"uid":2719,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T07:58:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果個個追完你都調頭走<br />\n就係你自己問題啦 關男人咩事</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我以為我地雙方有好感<br />\n原來係我自作多情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你鍾意人唔追番人？扮受害者屌你老味臭</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認真睇你呢個post嘅回應<br />\n俾人感覺真係好難頂 