1,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T08:01:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁似幾年前邊到睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n跟車太貼 走先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://warehouse-worker.blogspot.hk/2014/07/d.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwarehouse-worker.blogspot.hk%2F2014%2F07%2Fd.html&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8nIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=5b22a7d8\" target=\"_blank\">http://warehouse-worker.blogspot.hk/2014/07/d.html</a></blockquote><br />\n原來真係潮文，差唔多一模一樣咁copy：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.uwants.com/viewthread.php?tid=15259514\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.uwants.com%2Fviewthread.php%3Ftid%3D15259514&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8nIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=8f97bb29\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.uwants.com/viewthread.php?tid=15259514</a></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80f304e271d69aad0033fe2354cce62771bde9c1","tid":151771,"uid":72581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T08:01:53.000Z","msg":"你自己都話中意就一定會俾佢知<br />\n唔中意就friend zone <br />\n個男仔feel 到你friend zone 佢咪唔追囉"},{"pid":"23069b837ba36706fd43aa3dcca95cf4c837fcaf","tid":151771,"uid":8302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T08:02:17.000Z","msg":"雖然知係假，屌你老母 send msg又唔知你想點，模模糊糊咁，咪走囉仆街"},{"pid":"a139869206ff0ff250a84517dff95fcb7a0463d7","tid":151771,"uid":48942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T08:03:17.000Z","msg":"你會唔會主動搵人？<br />\n有啲男仔feel到自己對你黎講可有可無<br />\n索性搵個會珍惜自己嘅人"},{"pid":"7e0ebad80c6d2e0f4aaf1e5403fbe00a193aa6c7","tid":151771,"uid":42601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2