","msg":"樓豬姓黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe4a4af01f1e13d74058838c0b4ffc6f730b298c","tid":151771,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T08:24:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>條條仔你都唔啱，然後怪人放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無feel呀<br />\n一係就勁chur人 一係就勁痴身 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我鍾意既都唔鍾意我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇少D 韓劇啦，feel feel feel <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01ac26669cbced1f2f82fdb3004dd292271be69c","tid":151771,"uid":53775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T08:24:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一定要等人地追你?你肯定係啲扮矜持既女人要人表埋白先會答覆人 人地追得耐都覺得攰啦</blockquote><br />\n正常程序唔係咁咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"497ac06d91d89329df9bebe4f4bcb0491e5da5bd","tid":151771,"uid":1017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T08:28:52.000Z","msg":"feel到你冇意思咪唔追囉，呢個世界又唔係得你一個"},{"pid":"34c6fa3a920d0bd5441b6e61309eb8adecb1015a","tid":151771,"uid":38041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T08:29:51.000Z","msg":"負皮上一頁 內文睇都費時睇"},{"pid":"f18e9a332ca8e7562988f2f74fcca2fffd719198","tid":151771,"uid":19404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T08:31:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>負皮上一頁 內文睇都費時睇</blockquote><br />\nagger"},{"pid":"336c0929ad5bdea546ab1715c9d3365c07cdc246","tid":151771,"uid":34759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T08:32:04.000Z","msg":"試下拎個閪出來當八達通嘟"},{"pid":"4f353c5088d20889d365994b2dd46358533a35aa","tid":151771,"uid":30922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl